_sText:
This map is my first map that I’m releasing because I don’t think it’s not bad enough to share. I’ve been doing
a lot of practice and the only thing I need to work on is Skyboxes. If you could help me with this contact me
with the link below.
(steamcommunity.com/id/kyleistheshadow)
Name: measure_crysis_v1
Features: Custom Textures (let me know if you have issues with this *black & purple*)
On the roof of a brick building there is a orange texture with a body in it, it's a hint that you can go though
that wall and inside.
Breakable wall near T spawn, next to a ladder.
*My favorite*: The breachable door at T spawn, you'll see it there as a wooden door. Shoot at/near the 
handle to break the door open to go inside. Otherwise it will not open. (Pretty cool right? ya.)
Many advantages and engagement areas. Get to know the map and it should be fun.
Bots do pretty well with the map, give it a try. (they love the big building)
